    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introdução a PyAtSpi2</title>

      <para>
        The <application>PyAtSpi2</application> package contains
<application>Python</application> bindings for the core components of the
<application>GNOME</application> Accessibility.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

