    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalação de PyAtSpi2</title>

      <para>
        To build <application>PyAtSpi2</application> as a <application>Python
3</application> module, run the following commands:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr --with-python=/usr/bin/python3</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        Esse pacote não vem com uma suíte de teste.
      </para>

      <para>
        To install the <application>Python 3</application> module, run the following
command as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    </sect3>

